summary: Cleopatra Bodyslide Preset. Requires cbbe bodyslide.
descriptionHtml:
Cleopatra Bodyslide Preset. Requires cbbe bodyslide. NMM should install everything fine but if you have any problems just extract the file and drop it in your bodyslide presets folder.  Skyrim>Data>Calientetools>Sliderpresets. The pictures show both the 0 body weight and 100. 


[center][/center][center][/center][color=#00ff00]The Egyptian setting in the pictures is a world mod i have made and can be downloaded[/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85084/?][color=#e69138][size=6]HERE[/size][/color][/url]
